{
    "description_long": "This is a small, rectangular graveyard plot bordered by a tan stone wall and black iron fencing. Inside, there are several gray stone grave markers, including upright headstones, a cross, and a large, domed mausoleum with columns and a cross on top. A stone path made of irregular slabs runs through the center, leading from the entrance to the mausoleum. The ground is covered in green grass, with some patches of dirt and a few tufts of vegetation near the graves. The perimeter features two prominent stone pillars at the entrance, and a small wooden coffin is visible near the edge of the plot. The overall scene is somber and orderly, with clear separation between graves and pathways.",
    "description": "A small, walled graveyard with stone headstones, a domed mausoleum, iron fencing, and a central stone path on grassy ground.",
